@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qlwczc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.cos((v1 + 0.69 * tmp + 0.92)))
    v2 = v1
    v2 = v0
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.15) / 0.66) / wp.exp((v1 + 0.27 * v2 + 0.62)))
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
